<feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"> <id>blog.damonc.top/</id><title>仗剑天涯</title><subtitle>一个Unity3D、Unreal Engine、Godot等游戏引擎的博客，分享游戏开发经验、技术分享、游戏设计等技术文章。</subtitle> <updated>2026-06-22T23:46:13+08:00</updated> <author> <name>仗剑天涯</name> <uri>blog.damonc.top/</uri> </author><link rel="self" type="application/atom+xml" href="blog.damonc.top/feed.xml"/><link rel="alternate" type="text/html" hreflang="en" href="blog.damonc.top/"/> <generator uri="https://jekyllrb.com/" version="4.4.1">Jekyll</generator> <rights> © 2026 仗剑天涯 </rights> <icon>/assets/img/favicons/favicon.ico</icon> <logo>/assets/img/favicons/favicon-96x96.png</logo> <entry><title>固定管线到可编程管线的演进：Shader 为什么成为渲染系统的核心</title><link href="blog.damonc.top/posts/fixed-pipelines-2-programmable-pipelines/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="固定管线到可编程管线的演进：Shader 为什么成为渲染系统的核心" /><published>2026-06-22T10:00:00+08:00</published> <updated>2026-06-22T23:44:36+08:00</updated> <id>blog.damonc.top/posts/fixed-pipelines-2-programmable-pipelines/</id> <content type="text/html" src="blog.damonc.top/posts/fixed-pipelines-2-programmable-pipelines/" /> <author> <name>damonc-top</name> </author> <category term="Unity3D" /> <category term="Shader" /> <summary>从早期固定功能图形管线讲起，梳理 Vertex Shader、Pixel Shader、统一着色器架构、Compute Shader 和 Unity SRP 的演进逻辑，解释可编程管线为什么改变了实时渲染的表达方式与工程架构。</summary> </entry> <entry><title>GPU 是怎么画一帧的：从显卡原理到屏幕成像</title><link href="blog.damonc.top/posts/how-dose-the-gpu-render/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="GPU 是怎么画一帧的：从显卡原理到屏幕成像" /><published>2026-06-17T02:00:00+08:00</published> <updated>2026-06-22T23:44:36+08:00</updated> <id>blog.damonc.top/posts/how-dose-the-gpu-render/</id> <content type="text/html" src="blog.damonc.top/posts/how-dose-the-gpu-render/" /> <author> <name>damonc-top</name> </author> <category term="Unity3D" /> <category term="Shader" /> <summary>从 CPU 提交渲染命令开始，沿着 GPU 图形管线、光栅化、片元着色、帧缓冲、交换链和显示扫描，解释一帧图像如何被画到屏幕上。</summary> </entry> <entry><title>Unity AudioMixer 改为 AssetBundle 加载后 class ID 245 崩溃</title><link href="blog.damonc.top/posts/unity-audiomixer-assetbundle-class-id-245/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Unity AudioMixer 改为 AssetBundle 加载后 class ID 245 崩溃" /><published>2026-05-20T18:00:00+08:00</published> <updated>2026-05-20T18:00:00+08:00</updated> <id>blog.damonc.top/posts/unity-audiomixer-assetbundle-class-id-245/</id> <content type="text/html" src="blog.damonc.top/posts/unity-audiomixer-assetbundle-class-id-245/" /> <author> <name>damonc-top</name> </author> <category term="Unity3D" /> <category term="Bugs" /> <summary>记录 Unity 项目中 AudioMixer 从场景静态引用改为脚本 AssetBundle 加载后，在 Android IL2CPP 包上触发 Could not produce class with ID 245 的定位过程和 link.xml 修复方式。</summary> </entry> <entry><title>ComfyUI 游戏美术资产模板化生产流(一)：从管线骨架到三维控制模型</title><link href="blog.damonc.top/posts/comfyui-learning-roadmap/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="ComfyUI 游戏美术资产模板化生产流(一)：从管线骨架到三维控制模型" /><published>2026-05-19T23:00:00+08:00</published> <updated>2026-05-19T23:00:00+08:00</updated> <id>blog.damonc.top/posts/comfyui-learning-roadmap/</id> <content type="text/html" src="blog.damonc.top/posts/comfyui-learning-roadmap/" /> <author> <name>damonc-top</name> </author> <category term="AI" /> <category term="ComfyUI" /> <summary>系列第一章，记录两个半小时的 ComfyUI 系统学习过程，深入剖析 SD1.5 基础管线、LoRA 风格注入、img2img 内容驱动、ControlNet 结构约束的底层原理，以及关于约束粒度的思想实验。</summary> </entry> <entry><title>受保护文章示例</title><link href="blog.damonc.top/posts/protected-post-example/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="受保护文章示例" /><published>2026-03-25T10:00:00+08:00</published> <updated>2026-03-25T10:00:00+08:00</updated> <id>blog.damonc.top/posts/protected-post-example/</id> <content type="text/html" src="blog.damonc.top/posts/protected-post-example/" /> <author> <name>damonc-top</name> </author> <category term="AI" /> <category term="Claude Code" /> <summary>这是一个带密码保护的文章示例</summary> </entry> </feed>
